data.description: Welcome home! Sprawling on just under an acre this home boasts a stained fenced in backyard with 2 patios. Freshly painted exterior.Concrete pad for RV/Boat or additional parking. 11.5x20' shed to matches house, cozy front porch. Front living area offers a DR and Formal sitting room, while the kitchen is a dream. Backsplash installed, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops with an island that is great for entertaining. Eat in area overlooks living area featuring electric fireplace with stone/shiplap surround & custom mantel. Off the kitchen you will find a cozy spot in your sunroom to soak in the sunshine. Upstairs has all of the large bedrooms. Primary Bedroom has vaulted ceilings and a walkthrough closet that is huge. His and her sinks with soaking tub in PB. w/ 5 bedrooms and 3 full baths you will have plenty of space in this like new home! About 6 mins from the VA line located near shopping! Seller has an assumable loan at 2.75%, call me for more details!
